  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To address the exploding rates of early pregnancies, forced marriages, and sexual violence against girls in Tanganyika province due to the Covid-19 pandemic, we will educate 25 adolescent girl coordinators on laws against sexual violence and on women&apos;s rights, develop school education activities targeted to reduce and prevent sexual violence, and through girl-led radio and social media broadcasts, communicate critical information to the entire community, in particular to women and girls.</narrative>
  </description>
